Sweet Potato Burger

45 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

egg

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

main

Tags:

burgerhealthyeasy

Description

A delicious and hearty sweet potato burger packed with flavor and nutrition, perfect for any meal!

Ingredients

  • sweet potatoes: 2 large
  • black beans: 1 can
  • oats: 1 cup
  • onion: 1/2, finely chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • egg: 1
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • paprika: 1/2 tsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
